  "description": "I\u0026rsquo;ve been off Facebook for a bit, but just wanted to give a big \u0026ldquo;thank you\u0026rdquo; to the people who messaged me over the weekend, \u0026ldquo;congratulating\u0026rdquo; me on being correct about my claims that Bernie Sanders\u0026rsquo; campaign was supported \u0026amp; influenced by Russian interference, which were entirely proven by the indictments which were released last week.\nMy adamant stance that his campaign was supported by foreign powers and existed more to sabotage a legitimate election than anything else cost me a lot of friends, both on Facebook and in real-life.\n",
